<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cookie Policy - GiftedTrades</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900">
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg my-28">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-6">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: 16 November 2024</p>

        <p class="mb-4">
            Welcome to <span class="font-semibold">GiftedTrades</span>' Cookie Policy. This policy explains how
            we use cookies to enhance your experience on our cryptocurrency trading platform and your choices regarding
            their use.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">1. What are Cookies?</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
            Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit our platform. They help improve the
            functionality and security of the website and provide insights into how users interact with our platform.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
            We use cookies to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>Secure your sessions and safeguard your trading activities.</li>
            <li>Improve platform functionality and user experience.</li>
            <li>Analyze traffic and trading patterns to optimize performance.</li>
            <li>Provide personalized content, including real-time market data.</li>
            <li>Remember your preferences, such as preferred cryptocurrencies or trading settings.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
            The following types of cookies are used on our platform:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>
                <strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Necessary for account authentication, secure transactions, and core
                platform operations.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Analytical Cookies:</strong> Help us understand trading trends and user behavior to improve the
                platform.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Functionality Cookies:</strong> Save your account settings, such as language preferences or
                preferred trading pairs.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Marketing Cookies:</strong> Deliver targeted ads and promotions tailored to your trading
                interests.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
            You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings. Disabling essential cookies may limit your
            ability to use certain features, such as executing trades or viewing market data.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
            For detailed guidance on managing cookies, visit your browser's help section or check our dedicated <a
                href="#" class="text-blue-600 underline">Cookie Management Guide</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3 mt-6">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
            We may update this Cookie Policy periodically to reflect changes in technology, laws, or platform features.
            Please review this page regularly for updates.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4">
            If you have any questions about this policy, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@giftedtrades.com"
                class="text-blue-600 underline">contact us</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
